<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
</head>
<body>
<h1>Hello, <%= @current_user.name %></h1>
<p> Ticket ID <%= @ticket.unique_id %></p>
<p>The status of the ticket: <%= @ticket.issue %> has been updated to <% @ticket.statuses.each do |status| %><%= status.name %><% end %> by <%= @current_user.name %></p>
<p>Ticket Description: <%= @ticket.content %></p>
<p>Click <a href="<%= @url %>">here</a> to view the ticket.</p>
<p>Best regards,</p>
<p>Your Team</p>
</body>
</html>